# Connection to CPP Farm Store

Even though Court Archive is not a farm store, this Shopify setup still connects to the CPP Farm Store consulting project because it helps me think about product organization, homepage design, and customer experience. For both stores, the customer needs to quickly understand what is being sold, why it matters, and how to shop. Court Archive uses clear categories like training gear, recovery, accessories, and apparel, while CPP Farm Store could use a similar approach with produce, pantry items, plants, gifts, and seasonal bundles. Building this practice store helps me understand how Shopify can make a retail store easier to browse and more connected across online and offline channels.

